  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Dignifying Shelters and Essential Non-Food Items for Most Vulnerable Displaced People in Forkouloum and Amma 3 Displacement Sites in the Lac Province</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Due to the constant activity of non-state armed groups in the Lac Province, Chad, waves of people seeking shelter inland of the province are becoming more and more dramatic resulting in an increased crisis among the displaced people of the Lac Province. The project aims to mitigate this crisis in sites targeted by the humanitarian country team by distributing shelter and non-food essential items to 5,500 displaced people while using an integrated approach with the other humanitarian aid partners and ensuring a reliable mechanism for accountability to affected population.</narrative>
  </description>
